OL,3,CPolice warning after spike in courier
OL,4,Cscams as man loses #15,500
OL,6,FHampshire Police has issued an urgent
OL,7,Fwarning after a spike in courier scams
OL,8,Facross the region, with five cases in
OL,9,Fthe county in just one week.
OL,11,FDavid Spurling, in his 80s from
OL,12,FWinchester, was duped out of #15,500
OL,13,Fafter a call from someone claiming to
OL,14,Fbe an officer.
OL,16,FDavid says he is "furious" with the
OL,17,Fscammers and spoke about the ordeal to
OL,18,Fhelp prevent others from falling
OL,19,Fvictim.
