OL,6,FHe said: "I got a call from the police
OL,7,Fsaying there'd been fraudulent
OL,8,Factivity detected on my Tesco credit
OL,9,Fcard. They thought it was part of a
OL,10,Fwider conspiracy.
OL,12,F"He explained that they were an
OL,13,Fundercover operation trying to track
OL,14,Fdown a group of fraudsters comprising
OL,15,Fcounterfeit Euro notes and also money
OL,16,Flaundering."
