OL,3,CPolice warning after spike in courier
OL,4,Cscams as man loses #15,500
OL,6,FDavid withdrew several thousand pounds
OL,7,Fin Euros from foreign exchange
OL,8,Fcounters. The group involved faked
OL,9,Fidentity checks and pretended to
OL,10,Finsure his money.
OL,12,FHe was told it needed to be collected
OL,13,Ffor forensic examination by the police
OL,14,Fand a courier was arranged to collect
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,FMr Purling said: "The total amount
OL,18,Finvolved is a fairly staggering
OL,19,F#15,500. Just a staggering amount.
