OL,6,F"I'm sickened that in fact I've lost
OL,7,Fthis money, but I did it with the best
OL,8,Fof intentions. I genuinely thought I
OL,9,Fwas bringing these people to book."
OL,11,FDetective Constable Owain Davies,
OL,12,FHampshire Police Economic Crime Unit,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We have unfortunately had a
OL,14,Freal spike recently.
