OL,6,FThe Detective Constable said: "The
OL,7,Fmain two things that I think people
OL,8,Fneed to realise and understand is that
OL,9,Fone, police and the banks will never
OL,10,Fever ask for you to go and withdraw
OL,11,Fmoney, cash from your bank account,
OL,12,Fbuilding society account for us to
OL,13,Fcollect.
OL,15,F"We will never direct you to go to a
OL,16,Fshop to buy high-value jewellery or
OL,17,Fwatches and we'll never ask you to buy
OL,18,Fgold bullion that gets sent to your
OL,19,Fhouse."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
