OL,6,FThe recommendation to anyone who is
OL,7,Fconcerned about a potential scam, is
OL,8,Fto take the officer's name, rank and
OL,9,Fcollar number, hang up, and dial 101
OL,10,Ffrom a different phone to ensure the
OL,11,Fscammers are not still on the line.
OL,13,FDavid says they can be very convincing
OL,14,Fand he wants to prevent others from
OL,15,Fgetting conned.
