OL,6,FMr Spurling said: "I think this is
OL,7,Freally an insidious thing, why I am so
OL,8,Ffurious with these scammers is because
OL,9,Fthe police are one of the pillars of
OL,10,Four democracy and we're justly proud
OL,11,Fof them and this is making their job
OL,12,Ffar more difficult.
OL,14,F"I think they're just the pits. If I
OL,15,Fcan help a little bit in publicising
OL,16,Fthis and relieving people of probably
OL,17,Ffar more strain than I've gone
OL,18,Fthrough, I feel that will be a good
OL,19,Fthing."
